## AlInsightLocations variable

A dictionary of insight locations (as reported by AIMS and the locations service).

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
AlInsightLocations: {
    [locationId: string]: ({
        residency: string;
        residencyCaption: string;
        alternatives?: string[];
        logicalRegion: string;
    });
}
```
